1958;;A Certain Smile;;American;;Jean Negulesco;;Rossano Brazzi, Joan Fontaine, Bradford Dillman;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/A_Certain_Smile_(film);;In Paris, beautiful Dominique Vallon is involved with a young man, Bertrand Griot, until suddenly entering into an unwise week-long romance with his wealthy and married uncle, Luc Ferrand.